      "content": "everything is just so quiet now. i walk into the kitchen and i forget for a second that he isn't there, and then it hits me all over again. the house feels like it's empty, even when i'm in it. i don't even know why i bother getting out of bed or making coffee anymore. it feels like i'm just a ghost going through the motions of a life that doesn't even belong to me anymore.",
